import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'
import {AiFillHome} from 'react-icons/ai'
import {SideBarContainer, SideNavBar, SideNavItem, NavItemText} from './StyledComponents'

const SideBar = () => (
  <SideBarContainer>
    <SideNavBar>
      <Link to="/">
        <SideNavItem>
          <AiFillHome />
          <NavItemText></NavItemText>
        </SideNavItem>
      </Link>
    </SideNavBar>
  </SideBarContainer>
)
export default SideBar
